sentences: Thomas Harrison Miller Jr. (born September 27, 1970) is an American contemporary Christian music singer, songwriter and pastor.

sentences: Thomas Harrison Miller Jr. (born September 27, 1970) is an American contemporary Christian music singer, songwriter and pastor.
He is an executive pastor at Gateway Church in Southlake, Texas and was formerly the church's senior worship leader.
In 2003, Thomas became worship pastor at Gateway Church.
